parameters:
Zerachiel: This is the Tree of
Fantasia...

Sachia: It doesn't really look like a
big tree, does it?

Claudia: The dimensions of the internal
space are twisted by powerful elements.

Claudia: If you fall outside, you won't
be able to come back.

Rabi: Uooo... This is a terrifying
place...

Lala: Somewhere in this big tree, Lord
Ern is here...!!

Zerachiel: I heard from Mel that the
Tree of Fantasia is a trial.

Zerachiel: Those lacking power shall
only know death.
